title: Skill Emperor,combat king
summary: Skill Emperor,combat king Manhua The popular online novel “Lingwu Dizun” is finally adapted to Comics, which combines passion, fantasy and harem. He awakened the body of all spirits and became a physique of both spiritual and martial cultivation. After the competition ended, he was ruthlessly chased by the royal family on the way back to the Zongmen for refusing to join the royal power.
